description: Today I chose a shopping mall and got lucky as soon as I get out of my car. I stumbled upon a young guy who was there to buy a birthday present for his girlfriend. He bought her a very expensive perfume. The poor boy was willing to sacrifice his hard earned money to make her happy. He worked as a cashier so he didn´t have much to spare. I was sure he would like if I paid for the present and even throw some extra money on top. At first he got a bit scared by my offer. I thought that I lost him. But as I kept raising my offers, he calmed down a bit and agreed to fool around. Unfortunately, we got caught by a security guy and were made to leave. Thank god the boy lived nearby. I wouldn´t like to fuck him in that dirty garage anyways.
title: Czech Hunter 262
